The '''Lips''' are a body part around the [[mouth]]. There is a (usually larger) lower lip, and a smaller upper lip. They help us to eat, touch and speak.

Lips also show [[emotion]]s.

There are [[disease]]s that can affect the lips, for example [[herpes simplex]]. Someone can get this disease by [[kissing]] or having [[oral sex]].

